    • Three-hand Quartz: This electronic watch movement features a quartz crystal that oscillates when a current is applied to it.
    • Multifunction: Quartz movement typically built into three separate sub-eyes for the day of the week, date of the month and 24-hour time.
    • Chronograph: A multifunction watch with stopwatch functionality.
    • Strap Inner Circumference: 200 +/- 5 mm

    GIFTABLE TINS

    Our watch tins are ready to gift or collect. Weve spent decades perfecting our craft and creating watches that youll love to wear and collect.

    QUALITY MATERIALS

    • Our high-quality leather is known for its softness and ability to look good over time.
    • Stainless steel watch bracelets are extremely durable and can last the lifetime of a watch if properly maintained. We offer free watch adjustments in our Fossil Retail and Outlet Stores.
    • Silicone watch straps are waterproof and very comfortable to wear.

    INTERCHANGEABLE WATCH BANDS

    Theres no better way to keep your favorite looks fresh than with our swappable, versatile watch straps. Our quick release pins allow you to change up your look as often as you like while maintaining your signature style.

    WATER RESISTANT

    • 3ATM: withstands splashes or brief immersion in water but not swimming or bathing
    • 5 ATM: wearable around household sinks or while swimming in shallow water
    • 10 ATM: suitable for bathing, swimming or snorkeling, but not scuba diving

    Product description

    This men's Nate chronograph watch by Fossil is perfect for the adventure enthusiast in you. This watch boasts of a detail-packed matte black dial is accented with black applied numerals and arabics indexes, a date window, three sub-dials along with three crowns on its side. Encased in a solid, round, black stainless steel case, it is attached to a three link bracelet, fastened around your wrist using a traditional buckle, which makes this watch both-sturdy and fashionable. Dial width - 50 mm, Strap width - 24 mm, Strap Type - Stainless Steel, Dial Material - Stainless Steel, Water Resistance - 100 m, Movement Type - Quartz. Take a look at this analogue watch that will perfectly accessories any of your casual outfits.
